    双向链表的实现

    # 01、代码实现

    # -*- ecoding: utf-8 -*-
# @ModuleName: doublelinklist
# @Mail: 15717163552@163.com
# @Author: mozhouqiu
# @Time: 2022/5/22 14:07

class Node:
    def __init__(self,val):
        self.data = val
        self.pre = None
        self.next = None

class DobleLinkList:
    def __init__(self):
        self._head = None

    def is_empty(self):
        return self._head is None

    def length(self):
        cursor = self._head
        count = 0
        while cursor is not None:
            count += 1
            cursor = cursor.next
        return count

    def travel(self):
        cursor = self._head
        while cursor is not None:
            print(cursor.data)
            cursor = cursor.next

    def add(self,val):
        """链表头部插入"""
        node = Node(val)
        node.next = self._head
        self._head.pre = node
        self._head = node

    def append(self,val):
        """链表尾部插入"""
        node = Node(val)
        if self._head is None:
            self._head = node
        else:
            cursor = self._head
            while cursor.next is not None:
                cursor = cursor.next
            cursor.next = node
            node.pre = cursor

    def insert(self,index,val):
        node = Node(val)
        if index <= 0:
            self.add(node)
        elif index > (self.length() - 1):
            self.append(node)
        else:
            cursor = self._head
            count = 0
            while count < index:
                count += 1
                cursor = cursor.next
            node.next = cursor
            node.pre = cursor.pre
            cursor.pre.next = node
            cursor.pre= node

    def remove(self,val):
        """删除元素"""
        cursor = self._head
        while cursor is not None:
            if cursor.data == val:
                if cursor == self._head:
                    self._head = cursor.next
                    if cursor.next is not None:
                        cursor.next.pre = None
                    break
                else:
                    cursor.pre.next = cursor.next
                    if cursor.next is not None:
                        cursor.next.pre = cursor.pre
                    break
            else:
                cursor = cursor.next

    def search(self,val):
        """查询元素"""
        cursor = self._head
        while cursor.next is not None:
            if cursor.data == val:
                return True
            else:
                cursor = cursor.next
        else:
            return False


a = DobleLinkList()
a.append(1)
a.append(2)
a.append(3)
a.append(4)
a.append(5)
# a.travel()
a.add(6)
# a.travel()
a.insert(1,9)
a.remove(3)
a.travel()
